      <title>渣打银行认为印度储备银行降息周期“较浅”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/stanchart-sees-shallow-rbi-rate-cutting-cycle-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行印度金融市场主管兼南亚宏观交易主管 Parul Mittal Sinha 预计，印度储备银行将在 10 月和 12 月分别进行 25 个基点的“小幅降息周期”。她在“彭博市场：亚洲”节目中与 Paul Allen 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/stanchart-sees-shallow-rbi-rate-cutting-cycle-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 05:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
