      <title>英国金融家聘请 Lazard 就失败的赞比亚交易提供咨询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-financier-hires-lazard-to-advise-on-zambia-deal-that-soured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国国际投资有限公司 (British International Investment Plc) 已聘请 Lazard Inc. 为其对赞比亚肉类生产商的可转换优先股投资提供建议，此前该公司的价值已缩水逾三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-financier-hires-lazard-to-advise-on-zambia-deal-that-soured</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典房价有望从 2022 年的低迷中恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/swedish-housing-prices-on-track-to-recover-from-2022-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通胀冲击导致借贷成本上升，并导致房屋建筑几乎陷入停滞，瑞典房价已收回通胀冲击第一年所蒙受损失的近一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/swedish-housing-prices-on-track-to-recover-from-2022-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
